                        "body": "<div class=\"u-mb-3\"><b>User note:</b></div>\n<div class=\"u-mt-3\"><i><b>About this chapter:</b> Mechanical systems are a key element of any building. Chapter 28 regulates such systems by linking to the International Mechanical Code<sup>\u00ae </sup>and International Fuel Gas Code<sup>\u00ae</sup>, where details of mechanical system requirements are provided.</i></div>",
